Alembic migration history for the project database.

Create a revision:

    uv run alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"

Review the generated migration, then apply it with DATABASE_URL_ADMIN:

    uv run alembic upgrade head

After a migration creates a table, refresh restricted-role grants:

    uv run python -m scripts.configure_db_permissions

Application code must use DATABASE_URL_WRITE or DATABASE_URL_READ.
Tables not represented in project_dm.models.Base are treated as unmanaged and
will not be removed by autogenerated migrations.
